overview: Delve into the underground world of Chicano rap with this all-access documentary, which features exclusive music videos from top performers, live concert footage, sexy women and interviews with old-school pioneers as well as up-and-coming players. Big-name artists making appearances in this program include Lighter Shade of Brown, Conejo, Rude Boy, Sleepy Malo, Lil Crook, Sniper and O.G. Spanish Fly.
title: Southland's Most Wanted
